{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Mark Zuckerberg,"},{"time":2000,"text":"a journalist was asking him a question about the news feed."},{"time":5000,"text":"And the journalist was asking him,"},{"time":7000,"text":"\"Why is this so important?\""},{"time":9000,"text":"And Zuckerberg said,"},{"time":11000,"text":"\"A squirrel dying in your front yard"},{"time":13000,"text":"may be more relevant to your interests right now"},{"time":16000,"text":"than people dying in Africa.\""},{"time":19000,"text":"And I want to talk about"},{"time":21000,"text":"what a Web based on that idea of relevance might look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"So when I was growing up"},{"time":27000,"text":"in a really rural area in Maine,"},{"time":29000,"text":"the Internet meant something very different to me."},{"time":32000,"text":"It meant a connection to the world."},{"time":34000,"text":"It meant something that would connect us all together."},{"time":37000,"text":"And I was sure that it was going to be great for democracy"},{"time":40000,"text":"and for our society."},{"time":43000,"text":"But there's this shift"},{"time":45000,"text":"in how information is flowing online,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and it's invisible."},{"time":50000,"text":"And if we don't pay attention to it,"},{"time":52000,"text":"it could be a real problem."},{"time":55000,"text":"So I first noticed this in a place I spend a lot of time --"},{"time":58000,"text":"my Facebook page."},{"time":60000,"text":"I'm progressive, politically -- big surprise --"},{"time":63000,"text":"but I've always gone out of my way to meet conservatives."},{"time":65000,"text":"I like hearing what they're thinking about;"},{"time":67000,"text":"I like seeing what they link to;"},{"time":69000,"text":"I like learning a thing or two."},{"time":71000,"text":"And so I was surprised when I noticed one day"},{"time":74000,"text":"that the conservatives had disappeared from my Facebook feed."},{"time":78000,"text":"And what it turned out was going on"},{"time":80000,"text":"was that Facebook was looking at which links I clicked on,"},{"time":84000,"text":"and it was noticing that, actually,"},{"time":86000,"text":"I was clicking more on my liberal friends' links"},{"time":88000,"text":"than on my conservative friends' links."},{"time":91000,"text":"And without consulting me about it,"},{"time":93000,"text":"it had edited them out."},{"time":95000,"text":"They disappeared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"So Facebook isn't the only place"},{"time":101000,"text":"that's doing this kind of invisible, algorithmic"},{"time":103000,"text":"editing of the Web."},{"time":106000,"text":"Google's doing it too."},{"time":108000,"text":"If I search for something, and you search for something,"},{"time":111000,"text":"even right now at the very same time,"},{"time":113000,"text":"we may get very different search results."},{"time":116000,"text":"Even if you're logged out, one engineer told me,"},{"time":119000,"text":"there are 57 signals"},{"time":121000,"text":"that Google looks at --"},{"time":124000,"text":"everything from what kind of computer you're on"},{"time":127000,"text":"to what kind of browser you're using"},{"time":129000,"text":"to where you're located --"},{"time":131000,"text":"that it uses to personally tailor your query results."},{"time":134000,"text":"Think about it for a second:"},{"time":136000,"text":"there is no standard Google anymore."},{"time":140000,"text":"And you know, the funny thing about this is that it's hard to see."},{"time":143000,"text":"You can't see how different your search results are"},{"time":145000,"text":"from anyone else's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"But a couple of weeks ago,"},{"time":149000,"text":"I asked a bunch of friends to Google \"Egypt\""},{"time":152000,"text":"and to send me screen shots of what they got."},{"time":155000,"text":"So here's my friend Scott's screen shot."},{"time":159000,"text":"And here's my friend Daniel's screen shot."},{"time":162000,"text":"When you put them side-by-side,"},{"time":164000,"text":"you don't even have to read the links"},{"time":166000,"text":"to see how different these two pages are."},{"time":168000,"text":"But when you do read the links,"},{"time":170000,"text":"it's really quite remarkable."},{"time":174000,"text":"Daniel didn't get anything about the protests in Egypt at all"},{"time":177000,"text":"in his first page of Google results."},{"time":179000,"text":"Scott's results were full of them."},{"time":181000,"text":"And this was the big story of the day at that time."},{"time":183000,"text":"That's how different these results are becoming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"So it's not just Google and Facebook either."},{"time":189000,"text":"This is something that's sweeping the Web."},{"time":191000,"text":"There are a whole host of companies that are doing this kind of personalization."},{"time":194000,"text":"Yahoo News, the biggest news site on the Internet,"},{"time":197000,"text":"is now personalized -- different people get different things."},{"time":201000,"text":"Huffington Post, the Washington Post, the New York Times --"},{"time":204000,"text":"all flirting with personalization in various ways."},{"time":207000,"text":"And this moves us very quickly"},{"time":210000,"text":"toward a world in which"},{"time":212000,"text":"the Internet is showing us what it thinks we want to see,"},{"time":216000,"text":"but not necessarily what we need to see."},{"time":219000,"text":"As Eric Schmidt said,"},{"time":222000,"text":"\"It will be very hard for people to watch or consume something"},{"time":225000,"text":"that has not in some sense"},{"time":227000,"text":"been tailored for them.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":230000,"text":"So I do think this is a problem."},{"time":232000,"text":"And I think, if you take all of these filters together,"},{"time":235000,"text":"you take all these algorithms,"},{"time":237000,"text":"you get what I call a filter bubble."},{"time":241000,"text":"And your filter bubble is your own personal,"},{"time":244000,"text":"unique universe of information"},{"time":246000,"text":"that you live in online."},{"time":248000,"text":"And what's in your filter bubble"},{"time":251000,"text":"depends on who you are, and it depends on what you do."},{"time":254000,"text":"But the thing is that you don't decide what gets in."},{"time":258000,"text":"And more importantly,"},{"time":260000,"text":"you don't actually see what gets edited out."},{"time":263000,"text":"So one of the problems with the filter bubble"},{"time":265000,"text":"was discovered by some researchers at Netflix."},{"time":268000,"text":"And they were looking at the Netflix queues, and they noticed something kind of funny"},{"time":271000,"text":"that a lot of us probably have noticed,"},{"time":273000,"text":"which is there are some movies"},{"time":275000,"text":"that just sort of zip right up and out to our houses."},{"time":278000,"text":"They enter the queue, they just zip right out."},{"time":281000,"text":"So \"Iron Man\" zips right out,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and \"Waiting for Superman\""},{"time":285000,"text":"can wait for a really long time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"What they discovered"},{"time":289000,"text":"was that in our Netflix queues"},{"time":291000,"text":"there's this epic struggle going on"},{"time":294000,"text":"between our future aspirational selves"},{"time":297000,"text":"and our more impulsive present selves."},{"time":300000,"text":"You know we all want to be someone"},{"time":302000,"text":"who has watched \"Rashomon,\""},{"time":304000,"text":"but right now"},{"time":306000,"text":"we want to watch \"Ace Ventura\" for the fourth time."},{"time":309000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":312000,"text":"So the best editing gives us a bit of both."},{"time":314000,"text":"It gives us a little bit of Justin Bieber"},{"time":316000,"text":"and a little bit of Afghanistan."},{"time":318000,"text":"It gives us some information vegetables;"},{"time":320000,"text":"it gives us some information dessert."},{"time":323000,"text":"And the challenge with these kinds of algorithmic filters,"},{"time":325000,"text":"these personalized filters,"},{"time":327000,"text":"is that, because they're mainly looking"},{"time":329000,"text":"at what you click on first,"},{"time":333000,"text":"it can throw off that balance."},{"time":337000,"text":"And instead of a balanced information diet,"},{"time":340000,"text":"you can end up surrounded"},{"time":342000,"text":"by information junk food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"What this suggests"},{"time":346000,"text":"is actually that we may have the story about the Internet wrong."},{"time":349000,"text":"In a broadcast society --"},{"time":351000,"text":"this is how the founding mythology goes --"},{"time":353000,"text":"in a broadcast society,"},{"time":355000,"text":"there were these gatekeepers, the editors,"},{"time":357000,"text":"and they controlled the flows of information."},{"time":360000,"text":"And along came the Internet and it swept them out of the way,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and it allowed all of us to connect together,"},{"time":365000,"text":"and it was awesome."},{"time":367000,"text":"But that's not actually what's happening right now."},{"time":371000,"text":"What we're seeing is more of a passing of the torch"},{"time":374000,"text":"from human gatekeepers"},{"time":376000,"text":"to algorithmic ones."},{"time":379000,"text":"And the thing is that the algorithms"},{"time":382000,"text":"don't yet have the kind of embedded ethics"},{"time":385000,"text":"that the editors did."},{"time":388000,"text":"So if algorithms are going to curate the world for us,"},{"time":391000,"text":"if they're going to decide what we get to see and what we don't get to see,"},{"time":394000,"text":"then we need to make sure"},{"time":396000,"text":"that they're not just keyed to relevance."},{"time":399000,"text":"We need to make sure that they also show us things"},{"time":401000,"text":"that are uncomfortable or challenging or important --"},{"time":404000,"text":"this is what TED does --"},{"time":406000,"text":"other points of view."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408000,"text":"And the thing is, we've actually been here before"},{"time":410000,"text":"as a society."},{"time":413000,"text":"In 1915, it's not like newspapers were sweating a lot"},{"time":416000,"text":"about their civic responsibilities."},{"time":419000,"text":"Then people noticed"},{"time":421000,"text":"that they were doing something really important."},{"time":424000,"text":"That, in fact, you couldn't have"},{"time":426000,"text":"a functioning democracy"},{"time":428000,"text":"if citizens didn't get a good flow of information,"},{"time":433000,"text":"that the newspapers were critical because they were acting as the filter,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and then journalistic ethics developed."},{"time":438000,"text":"It wasn't perfect,"},{"time":440000,"text":"but it got us through the last century."},{"time":443000,"text":"And so now,"},{"time":445000,"text":"we're kind of back in 1915 on the Web."},{"time":449000,"text":"And we need the new gatekeepers"},{"time":452000,"text":"to encode that kind of responsibility"},{"time":454000,"text":"into the code that they're writing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"I know that there are a lot of people here from Facebook and from Google --"},{"time":459000,"text":"Larry and Sergey --"},{"time":461000,"text":"people who have helped build the Web as it is,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and I'm grateful for that."},{"time":465000,"text":"But we really need you to make sure"},{"time":468000,"text":"that these algorithms have encoded in them"},{"time":471000,"text":"a sense of the public life, a sense of civic responsibility."},{"time":474000,"text":"We need you to make sure that they're transparent enough"},{"time":477000,"text":"that we can see what the rules are"},{"time":479000,"text":"that determine what gets through our filters."},{"time":482000,"text":"And we need you to give us some control"},{"time":484000,"text":"so that we can decide"},{"time":486000,"text":"what gets through and what doesn't."},{"time":489000,"text":"Because I think"},{"time":491000,"text":"we really need the Internet to be that thing"},{"time":493000,"text":"that we all dreamed of it being."},{"time":495000,"text":"We need it to connect us all together."},{"time":498000,"text":"We need it to introduce us to new ideas"},{"time":501000,"text":"and new people and different perspectives."},{"time":505000,"text":"And it's not going to do that"},{"time":507000,"text":"if it leaves us all isolated in a Web of one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}